  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\n\n### User Story\n\nAs a user, I want to see Status looks nicely on different devices.\n\n### Description\n\n*Type*: Bug\n*Summary*: There are several places when keyboard\\values\\screens are overlapping\n\n1) Sign Up process  (set up name) \n<img width=\"225\" alt=\"new\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/43585352-9298146e-966d-11e8-91e2-8a18ab06ad95.png\">\n\n 2) Back Up Recovery Prase (step 1)\n<img width=\"226\" alt=\"no_padding\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/43585428-c9173aa6-966d-11e8-8430-e2b871ff1215.png\">\n3) Amount and Total fee overlapped by keyboard on \"Transaction Fee\".\n<img width=\"220\" alt=\"tot_fee\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/43585985-182ded3c-966f-11e8-8387-ed485016b133.png\">\n\n4) Let's get set up wallet screen\n<img width=\"226\" alt=\"af\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/43586153-8ab3e906-966f-11e8-85a8-a7bd254d6564.png\">\n\n5) welcome to Status screen is too big\n<img width=\"225\" alt=\"welc_scr\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/43586254-ceb2f778-966f-11e8-990a-2051983fd52e.png\">\n\n*NOTE:* couldn't replicate on Android with similar resolution\n\n### Additional Information\n* Status version: nightly 02.08.18\n* Operating System: iOS (IPhone 5s)",
